    "Hence, SHERPA allows to directly assess whether a certain component indexes a neural mechanism and to which degree.",
    "We suggest presenting the SHERPA results in their original form, as they are intuitively understandable; for example: \"We found that the SHERPA scores for the [ERP component]",
